86 void SimObjController::onCollision(CollisionEvent &evt)
87 {
88  // Get name of entity which is touched by the robot
89  const std::vector<std::string> & with = evt.getWith();
90  // Get parts of the robot which is touched by the entity
91  const std::vector<std::string> & mparts = evt.getMyParts();
92  sig_ros::OnCollision msg;
93  for (int i=0; i < with.size(); i++) {
94  msg.name = with[i];
95  msg.part = mparts[i];
96  onCollision_pub.publish(msg);
97  }
98 }
